[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0252","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0252.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0282","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9149,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10831}}","description":"TalentSoft Web+ 购物车应用中的 webpsvr 守护进程在处理 webplus CGI 程序请求时，未对用户输入的路径进行充分校验，导致远程攻击者可通过在请求中插入\"..\"(点点)目录遍历序列，突破 Web 根目录限制访问服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Web+ 4.x 版本，攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可读取如密码文件、配置文件等敏感内容，可能造成信息泄露，为后续进一步入侵提供条件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0282"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:23.500","remediation":"建议立即安装 TalentSoft 官方发布的 Webplus46p 安全补丁（ftp://ftp.talentsoft.com/Download/Webplus/Unix/Patches/Webplus46p%20Read%20me.html），将受影响版本升级至修补后的版本。如无法立即安装补丁，可在 Web 服务器前端部署 WAF 规则，拦截 webplus CGI 程序请求中包含 `..` 或 `%2e%2e` 路径穿越序列的 HTTP 请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0050.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1102","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19842","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0282.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0282","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0282.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0282.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-3j9x-r422-3rxr/GHSA-3j9x-r422-3rxr.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webplus.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0282.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001283.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0252.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0235","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0235.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0262","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9171,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10856}}","description":"AVM KEN! ISDN 代理服务器 1.3.10 和 1.4.30 版本存在远程拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过发送畸形请求导致服务崩溃，使合法用户无法访问。该漏洞源于服务器对恶意构造的请求处理不当，无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响使用受影响版本 ISDN 代理服务的系统可用性。CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中等危害级别。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0262"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:20.893","remediation":"升级 AVM KEN! ISDN Proxy 服务器到官方修复版本（1.4.30 之后的安全更新版本），可通过 AVM 官网下载固件/软件更新包进行升级。如无法立即升级，应在边界防火墙或路由器上限制对 KEN! ISDN Proxy 服务端口（TCP 80/443 及 ISDN 代理端口）的外部访问，仅允许受信任的内部网络地址连接，以缓解远程拒绝服务攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0073.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1103","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=383085010.956159226625.JavaMail.root%40web305-mc.mail.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19843","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0262.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0262","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0262.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0262.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vx5q-wxf4-cq9p/GHSA-vx5q-wxf4-cq9p.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/ken_segfault.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0262.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4e3cd672-dbc1-43c9-93f1-8d06acec952e.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ce9ef916bfcfa71e15bd79861b0ea3312f7ed373/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0235.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0234","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0234.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0261","title":"AVM KEN! 网页服务器 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"AVM KEN! 设备内置的 Web 服务器存在目录遍历（../ 点号攻击）漏洞，未能正确对用户输入的路径进行规范化校验。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标设备的 Web 服务端口发送包含\"..\"序列的特制 HTTP 请求，即可绕过目录限制读取服务器根目录之外的任意文件，如配置文件、口令文件等敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行 AVM KEN! 固件并开启 Web 管理界面的设备，攻击条件为攻击者能通过网络访问目标设备的 HTTP 服务，利用方式简单，仅需构造恶意 URL 即可实现信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0261"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:20.763","remediation":"立即将 AVM KEN! 远程访问软件升级至官方修复版本（固件/程序版本 3.30 及以上，具体以 AVM 发布的安全更新为准）。升级前可在路由器或防火墙侧关闭 KEN! 远程 Web 访问功能，或仅允许受信任 IP 通过端口过滤访问该服务，以临时缓解任意文件读取风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0073.html","http://www.osvdb.org/1282","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1103","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=383085010.956159226625.JavaMail.root%40web305-mc.mail.com","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8f7915616bad1c7280e28216588ab0258074928/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0261.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0261","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0261.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6f1dc1488b4a75cccf07339e6a0f0ab45fc38ad/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0261.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3pjj-9jv7-w6xw/GHSA-3pjj-9jv7-w6xw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0261.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--261e4164-975e-4f25-bd65-e490f8425a18.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/54a49c35dfc49a19cf6de178ce37c0c006f4fb21/2000.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--261e4164-975e-4f25-bd65-e490f8425a18.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0234.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0234.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0234.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0233","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0233.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0259","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10796,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10820}}","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系统中 OffloadModExpo 组件所使用的 Cryptography\\Offload 注册表键存在默认权限配置不当的漏洞。该注册表键的访问控制权限设置过于宽松，导致本地已登录的普通用户能够读取或修改该键值。由于该键值中存储了其他用户的加密密钥材料，本地用户可利用此缺陷获取他人的私钥等敏感密钥信息，从而破坏系统加密机制的安全性。攻击条件为攻击者需在目标主机上拥有本地账户并能够登录系统，无需特殊权限即可访问该注册表键。影响范围涵盖运行 Windows NT 4.0 及其终端服务（Terminal Server）的服务器与工作站，危害等级为中高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0259"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:20.513","remediation":"直接升级 Windows NT 4.0 到 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本，更新安全补丁程序，并重置 Cryptogaphry\\Offload 注册表关键权限为安全配置，避免本地用户获取其他用户密钥。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1105","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-024","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8f7915616bad1c7280e28216588ab0258074928/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0259","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0259.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ea13d8ca97b52327fe351b64da51866911834231/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0259.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pqj9-rmm9-j2pp/GHSA-pqj9-rmm9-j2pp.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0259.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001281.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--354cac40-c4cf-4d5c-92e5-9da3e0e14b4b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0233.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0232","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0232.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0258","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9145,\"outputTokens\":16,\"totalTokens\":10825}}","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 和 5.0 版本在处理包含大量转义字符的 URL 请求时存在输入验证缺陷，远程未认证攻击者可通过发送包含大量转义字符的恶意 URL 请求（即 \"Myriad Escaped Characters\" 漏洞），导致 IIS 服务消耗过多 CPU 资源而拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 和 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5（高危），属于输入验证不当（CWE-20）类型。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，通过发送大量包含转义字符的 URL 请求消耗服务器 CPU 资源，导致服务拒绝。Microsoft 已发布安全更新修复此漏洞，建议升级至修补版本或应用官方补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0258"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:20.377","remediation":"建议升级至 Microsoft IIS 5.0 后续版本（SP1 及以上）或 IIS 6.0，并安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-078 提供的补丁（KB272760）。若无法立即升级，可在 IIS 配置中限制最大 URL 长度或在防火墙层面限制 URL 长度与转义字符数量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1101","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-023"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0232.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0276","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0276.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0288","title":"Infonautics getdoc.cgi 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Infonautics 的 getdoc.cgi 脚本存在安全绕过漏洞，远程攻击者通过修改表单变量（form variable）即可绕过文档访问的支付验证阶段，未经授权获取受限文档内容。该漏洞源于服务端未对用户提交的表单参数进行充分校验，攻击者无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0288"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"在 getdoc.cgi 的服务端支付验证逻辑中增加会话状态校验，所有支付确认须在后端 session 中标记并通过签名校验防止篡改，禁止仅依赖前端表单变量判断支付状态。如该 CGI 组件已无维护且无替代版本，建议直接停用或替换为支持服务端支付校验的文档管理系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0049.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0276.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0777","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0777.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0253","title":"Dansie Shopping Cart 购物车 cart.pl 隐藏表单字段篡改漏洞","description":"dansie 购物车应用程序的 cart.pl 脚本在处理订单提交时，未对 HTTP 请求中的隐藏表单字段进行服务端校验，远程攻击者可在提交订单时通过修改隐藏字段（如商品单价、数量、收货地址等购买信息）来篡改交易数据。该漏洞影响所有使用 cart.pl 搭建的在线商店，攻击者无需身份认证，只需构造包含伪造隐藏字段的表单请求即可利用，可导致商品价格被恶意降低或订单信息被篡改，造成商家经济损失与数据完整性破坏。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0253"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"该漏洞源于 cart.pl 信任客户端提交的隐藏表单字段。修复方法：1）升级到 Dansie Shopping Cart 的修复版本（1.1 及以上，发布于 2000 年 4 月），可从厂商站点 http://www.dansie.net 获取；2）临时措施：修改 cart.pl 源码，强制在服务端以会话中保存的价格和商品信息重新计算订单总额，忽略客户端提交的隐藏字段；3）对单价、数量等关键字段增加服务端校验与范围检查；4）如无法升级，建议停用 cart.pl 并迁移至受维护的现代购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1115","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4621"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0777.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0228","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0228.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0252","title":"Dansie 购物车 cart.pl 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Dansie Shopping Cart 应用的 cart.pl 脚本存在远程命令执行漏洞，攻击者可通过在 Web 表单变量中注入 Shell 元字符（如反引号、管道符、分号、&& 等），将恶意系统命令嵌入表单输入。当应用程序未对用户提交的数据进行充分过滤与转义时，这些命令将在服务器端被 shell 执行。该漏洞影响部署了 Dansie Shopping Cart 的 Web 站点，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，可导致服务器敏感信息泄露、网站内容被篡改甚至服务器被完全控制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0252"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-11","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"升级到修复了该漏洞的 Dansie Shopping Cart 新版本；若无法立即升级，应在 cart.pl 中对所有表单变量使用严格的输入校验与转义（如过滤分号、管道符、反引号等 Shell 元字符），避免将用户输入直接传入 system、exec 等函数；同时在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）配置中禁用 CGI 脚本的危险命令执行能力，并部署 Web 应用防火墙拦截包含 Shell 元字符的恶意请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0051.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1115","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4975"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0228.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0284","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0284.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0294","title":"FreeBSD healthd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统的 healthd 健康监控守护进程存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向 healthd 发送特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响运行 healthd 的 FreeBSD 系统，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级至已修复版本或禁用 healthd 服务以缓解风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0294"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:25.057","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至包含 healthd 漏洞修复版本（如 FreeBSD 3.4-RELEASE 之后的安全补丁版），或在 /etc/rc.conf 中将 moused_enable 设为 NO 以禁用 healthd 服务，限制本地用户执行权限以降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/606","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1107","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/advisory.html?id=2162"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0284.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0246","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0246.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0276","title":"Be BeOS 4.5/5.0 无效系统调用拒绝服务漏洞","description":"tags.<value>BeOS 4.5 和 5.0 版本中存在无效系统调用漏洞，本地攻击者可通过构造畸形的直接系统调用并利用中断 37 触发异常，导致系统服务崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 BeOS 4.5 和 5.0 版本，攻击者需具有本地访问权限才能利用此漏洞。成功利用后，系统将无法正常运行，造成服务中断，用户应升级到修复版本以消除风险。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0276"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:22.743","remediation":"建议将受影响的 BeOS 系统升级至 Be 官方发布的修复版本（BeOS 5.0.3 或后续补丁），以消除中断 37 的畸形系统调用处理缺陷。若暂无法升级，应限制普通本地用户权限、禁止非授权用户登录系统控制台，并通过移除或限制对内核直接系统调用接口的访问作为临时缓解措施，避免本地用户触发拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1098","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=20000410131628.659.qmail%40securityfocus.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19840","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2aa0c2dcb1730150467a1bc57cd9b2ece96310af/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0276.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0276","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0276.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/419b5e73717835e3c91c8f5fe969933e4b2e142e/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0276.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wwrg-82fc-4xc8/GHSA-wwrg-82fc-4xc8.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0276.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/b00846651d73ce227da89de12b15251a83e2ba27/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0246.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0244","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0244.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0275","title":"CRYPTOCard CRYPTOAdmin for PalmOS PIN 弱加密漏洞","description":"CRYPTOCard CRYPTOAdmin 4.1 中用于 PalmOS 的 CryptoAdmin 组件存在弱加密漏洞，其在存储用户的 PIN 码时采用了强度不足的加密算法。攻击者一旦获得目标设备上的 .PDB 数据库文件，即可通过破解其中的弱加密还原出用户 PIN 码，进而生成有效的 PT-1 令牌，实现对身份认证机制的绕过。该漏洞影响使用 CRYPTOCard CRYPTOAdmin 4.1 的 PalmOS 环境，攻击条件为攻击者需具备对本地 .PDB 文件的访问权限，利用方式为离线破解 PIN 后伪造合法认证令牌，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级为低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0275"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:22.627","remediation":"建议立即升级到 CRYPTOCard 官方发布的修复版本（4.1 之后已采用强加密的版本，联系厂商获取最新 CryptoAdmin 更新），替换使用弱加密存储 PIN 的旧版程序。在升级前，应避免将 CryptoAdmin 的 .PDB 数据文件存放于未受保护的设备上，通过 PalmOS 设备密码或文件加密对 .PDB 文件进行额外保护，并限制对设备的物理与同步访问，防止攻击者获取文件后离线破解 PIN 并伪造 PT-1 令牌。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0033.html","http://www.l0pht.com/advisories/cc-pinextract.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1097","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19839","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0275.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/50cb0f51a2a6988cb2c3b9e8c611d8b1e75d6a00/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0275.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0275","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/2000/CVE-2000-0275.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0275.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j3qx-3h5c-5hvp/GHSA-j3qx-3h5c-5hvp.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0275.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1097/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0244.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0242","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0242.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0274","title":"Linux Trustees 内核补丁长路径名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux trustees 内核安全补丁在处理超长文件或目录路径名时存在缺陷，攻击者通过访问具有超长名称的文件或目录即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致系统内核崩溃或不可用。该漏洞仅在本地可访问系统的攻击条件下可被利用，影响安装了 trustees 补丁的 Linux 系统，造成本地拒绝服务（DoS）后果。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0274"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-10","updated":"2020-06-16","remediation":"移除或更新 Linux trustees 内核补丁至无此缺陷的最新版本，或禁用 trustees 对超长路径名的特殊处理机制，确保系统不加载存在该缺陷的补丁版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0274","https://web.archive.org/web/2000/http://www.braysystems.com/linux/trustees.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0035.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1096"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0242.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0242.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0242.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0256","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0256.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0273","title":"Symantec pcAnywhere 登录重置拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Symantec pcAnywhere 8.0/9.0 版本存在登录重置拒绝服务漏洞，远程未授权攻击者可在 pcAnywhere 提供登录提示前主动终止连接，导致服务拒绝响应，导致远程控制服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Symantec pcAnywhere 8.0 和 9.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，仅需在登录提示出现前中断 TCP 连接即可触发拒绝服务，导致远程控制服务停止响应，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中危级别拒绝服务漏洞。Symantec 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议用户升级至修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0273"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:22.387","remediation":"建议升级 Symantec pcAnywhere 至 9.0.1 或更高版本（Symantec 已发布补丁修复该登录重置拒绝服务漏洞）。若暂时无法升级，可在防火墙层面限制 TCP 5631/5632 端口仅允许可信 IP 访问，或暂时禁用 pcAnywhere 服务直到应用补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0031.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1095","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1f3f1d799c1c9e44bc999093e18341513cabfa3f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0273.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0273","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0273.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/fb79aaf8eeeb3ec551114292cd7a8693e166aee6/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0273.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g592-cwxj-fv67/GHSA-g592-cwxj-fv67.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0273.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001271.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1ae26e59-e1a5-4031-89c1-e2ee8c0f2ca6.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0256.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0249","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0249.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0279","title":"Be BeOS 畸形IP数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BeOS 操作系统（4.0、4.5 及 5.0 版本）在处理网络数据包时存在拒绝服务漏洞。其网络协议栈未对数据包长度字段进行充分校验，当远程攻击者向目标系统发送长度字段小于协议头实际长度的特殊畸形数据包时，系统会因解析错误而耗尽资源或崩溃。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击者可借由网络远程发送特制报文触发，导致受影响主机无法提供正常网络服务，影响范围覆盖上述 BeOS 版本的联网设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0279"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:23.117","remediation":"建议将受影响的 BeOS 4.0/4.0.1/4.5/5.0 升级至 Be 官方发布的 BeOS 5.0.3 或后续修复版本（可通过 BeBits/官方更新渠道获取）。如暂无法升级，可在边界防火墙或路由器上丢弃分片异常、IP 头长度字段小于实际头部的畸形数据包，并在上游网络对来源 IP 做限速与过滤，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0029.html","http://bebugs.be.com/devbugs/detail.php3?oid=2505312","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1100","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19841","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0279.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0279","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0279.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/666a3c9c944f5ed9f7d7ff0aa29b047387ce02f3/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0279.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf4g-4vxr-q8px/GHSA-rf4g-4vxr-q8px.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0279.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--712755d6-06ba-4e6a-ad3a-52dd3b3274dd.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0249.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0289","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0289.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0298","title":"Microsoft Windows 2000 无人值守预安装权限设置不当漏洞","description":"Windows 2000 无人值守预安装功能在启用 OEMPreinstall 选项时，会将 All Users 及 Default Users 目录设置为不安全的权限，导致本地攻击者可利用该配置缺陷访问或篡改其他用户的文件及设置。攻击者需具备本地登录权限，通过修改共享目录中的配置文件实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows 2000 系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0298"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"手动修复受影响的 All Users 和 Default Users 目录权限：设置为仅允许 Administrators 和 SYSTEM 完全控制，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的写入权限。避免使用 OEMPreinstall 选项进行无人值守安装，改用 Sysprep 或通过安全模板应用正确的 NTFS 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/2000-q2/0027.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1758","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4278"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0289.toml"}]